{"tid":1597313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[美國贏左]  萬國郵政聯盟通過終端郵費改革　美指可阻中國以低成本發展網購","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T12:57:14.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cba7fe59f6331f072b83e2d3de50b8e054110250","tid":1597313,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"萬國郵政聯盟通過終端郵費改革　美指可阻中國以低成本發展網購<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=364155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364155&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=481bb232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364155&h=31e0ed4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=364155</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】萬國郵政聯盟成員在美國威脅退出下達成折衷方案，同意分階段改革，允許成員國自訂終端郵費，美國將於明年中實施。白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅稱，新制度可杜絕中國電子商貿利用郵費優惠，低成本發展網購業務。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國旗下負責協調各國郵政業務、監管國際郵遞價格的萬國郵政聯盟，在日內瓦舉行緊急會議。成員以口頭方式，通過分階段實施的終端郵費改革方案，容許像美國般，每年處理郵件量超過七萬五千公噸的國家，在明年中自訂終端郵費，即派送外國郵件收取的費用，其他國家按郵件量，五年內逐步自訂收費。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行機制，一件從外國寄到的郵包，抵埗後最後一程運輸是由當地郵政負責，這筆終端郵費，各國是按萬國郵政的計算支付，發展中國家享有優惠。<br />\n<br />\n美國自去年開始投訴中國等國家，利用優惠發展網購業務，以較低成本把貨物運到美國。除了美國本土公司面對不公平競爭，郵費成本差額更要由美國政府補貼每年高達五億美元，美國威脅如果不改革就會退會。<br />\n<br />\n白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅歡迎表決結果，指可以杜絕中國拿好處。<br />\n<br />\n萬國郵政聯盟有192個成員，今次是聯盟成立145年來，第三次召開緊急會議。在首日會議上，成員國否決了美國提出的一步到位方案，獲通過的折衷方案，則由包括中國在內的34個成員國商討得來。"},{"pid":"8fdd3ae9e62a5c7ab159806023108217319c6d73","tid":1597313,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第六期牆紙］ 百日抗爭運動，願榮光終歸香港<br />\n第六期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1</a><br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=13c119c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喜歡的話請記得訂閱</span>"},{"pid":"375404408ff332412f344cad271b989733126648","tid":1597313,"uid":170438,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"尾國人咪俾多d 郵費囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e66c451e23734a613f78138339a9e6f39251eeb","tid":1597313,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"375404408ff332412f344cad271b989733126648","tid":1597313,"uid":170438,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"尾國人咪俾多d 郵費囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:43:23.000Z","msg":"起底，負皮，block得"},{"pid":"a6fd3c433f1d95d06e9ebf0150583908f1d83bed","tid":1597313,"uid":224882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"牙侵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6eddfdb9863f70